Subject: [PATCH v2 2/2] [media] em28xx: support for Hauppauge WinTV-dualHD
 01595 ATSC/QAM
Message-ID: <20161218025523.zt3hhagvaidxz7sh@whisper>
MIME-Version: 1.0
